    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E92 M3 powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8. This atmospheric power plant features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise six-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Recent service includes documented rod bearing replacement and new throttle body actuators, addressing the primary wear points of this high-performance mill. The chassis retains its factory-tuned kinematics with functional Electronic Damper Control (EDC). While the paint shows minor road-rash consistent with its mileage, the structural integrity and powertrain synchronization remain excellent for the discerning driver.",
